Package org.opensaml.profile.context.navigate

Functions for navigating profile context information.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CurrentOrPreviousEventLookup
    Access either current or previous event from context tree.
    InboundMessageContextLookup
    A ContextDataLookupFunction that returns the inbound MessageContext for a ProfileRequestContext.
    OutboundMessageContextLookup
    A ContextDataLookupFunction that returns the outbound MessageContext for a ProfileRequestContext.
    ParentProfileRequestContextLookup<StartContext extends BaseContext>
    A convenience subtype of RecursiveTypedParentContextLookup which returns the ProfileRequestContext parent of the target BaseContext.
    ProfileIdLookup
    A ContextDataLookupFunction that returns the profile ID for a ProfileRequestContext.
